::Battera::

She woke up and stretched her arms.  She got up and walked around her 
room for a bit.  She looked at the door for a moment.  She remembered 
what she had said to Rex and Firearm.  She said she wou;dn't bother 
them any more.  She looked at her friut bowl and saw it was empty.
She walked over to the table where the bowl was resting.  She looked 
at it and picked it up.  She went to the door and opened it.  She 
walked down the hallway and to the messhall.  She put the bowl in the 
food dispencer and waited for it to fill with fruit.  When it was 
finished, she took her bowl left the messhall.  She went down the 
hallway to her room.
